                     scope="external">part 12</xref>
            </ph>
            <ph id="asuuhw2j" rev="Revised 18, March 2022">procedures for the acquisition of commercial items, when a multiple-award contract is contemplated and task orders or delivery orders placed under the contract may be valued at $10 million or more.</ph>
